Package: hextor
Architecture: any
Provides: irc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, hextor-common (= ${source:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, libotr5
Recommends: gvfs-bin
Suggests: unifont
Description: IRC client for X based on HexChat, X-Chat 2
 Hextor is a graphical IRC client with a GTK+ GUI. Features include Python
 (2 and 3) and Perl scripting support, a plugin API, multiple server/channel
 windows, spell checking, multiple authentication methods including SASL,
 and customizable notifications. For more information on IRC,
 see http://irchelp.org/.

Package: hextor-common
Architecture: all
Provides: irc
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: hextor
Description: Common files for Hextor
 This package includes documentation, headers, and locale files for the
 Debian Hextor packages that are common for all architectures. Hextor is a
 popular and featureful IRC client with a GTK+ GUI. For more information on
 IRC, see http://irchelp.org/.
